1. Create controller to create charge and internal return url
    - redirect_url GET /opn-payment/{orderId}

2. Create a POST method to create charge from front end to backend end
    - POST /opn-payment/charge/{orderId}
    - redirect_url GET /opn-payment/complete/{orderId}

2. handle redirect url and qr code in frontend payment.blade.php
3. handle redirect url after payment completed to update the charge status